# Customer Segmentation & Predictive Marketing Analytics

## Overview
This project analyzes marketing datasets to identify customer behavior patterns, perform segmentation analysis, and develop predictive analytics models using machine learning techniques.

The workflow combines exploratory analysis, dimensionality reduction, clustering, regression analysis, and ensemble modeling to generate data-driven marketing insights.

---

## Objectives
- Analyze customer and marketing behavior patterns
- Perform customer segmentation using clustering techniques
- Apply dimensionality reduction using PCA
- Build predictive analytics models for marketing insights
- Compare multiple analytical and machine learning techniques

---

## Dataset Information
- Dataset Size: 2,240 records
- Dataset Type: Marketing and customer behavior data
- Source: Kaggle Marketing Dataset

Variables Include:
- Customer demographics
- Campaign interactions
- Purchase behavior
- Marketing response indicators

